(13, 'Terns at Whatipu Beach', '&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;a title=&quot;Terns at Whatipu Beach&quot; href=&quot;http://www.aucklanddailyphoto.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/01102012-4254-1-1024.jpg&quot; rel=&quot;lightbox&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;aligncenter size-full wp-image-8480&quot; title=&quot;Terns at Whatipu Beach&quot; src=&quot;http://www.aucklanddailyphoto.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/01102012-4254-1.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;Terns at Whatipu Beach&quot; width=&quot;720&quot; height=&quot;432&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\nTerns at Whatipu Beach silhouetted against a blue spring sky&lt;br /&gt;\nClick image to enlarge&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;Today is theme day for the Daily photo community: &ldquo;Silhouette&rdquo;&lt;br /&gt;\n&lt;a href=&quot;http://cdpbthemeday.blogspot.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Click here to visit all other participants!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n', '&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;a title=&quot;Terns at Whatipu Beach&quot; href=&quot;http://www.aucklanddailyphoto.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/01102012-4254-1-1024.jpg&quot; rel=&quot;lightbox&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;aligncenter size-full wp-image-8480&quot; title=&quot;Terns at Whatipu Beach&quot; src=&quot;http://www.aucklanddailyphoto.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/01102012-4254-1.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;Terns at Whatipu Beach&quot; width=&quot;720&quot; height=&quot;432&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\nTerns at Whatipu Beach silhouetted against a blue spring sky&lt;br /&gt;\nClick image to enlarge&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;Today is theme day for the Daily photo community: &ldquo;Silhouette&rdquo;&lt;br /&gt;\n&lt;a href=&quot;http://cdpbthemeday.blogspot.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Click here to visit all other participants!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n', 'Lachezar', '2012-10-06 22:54:50', 'http://www.aucklanddailyphoto.com/2012/10/01/terns-at-whatipu-bea